reviewText: This cd did not work. It was from a library and there was some kind of block.
i got it for my 3rd granddaughter...she LOVES miss patty cake...everytime she comes to grandma's house she loves to watch it with her little sister.....they do the actions as well as sing along
I bought this video when my daughter was 1 yr old.  She still watches it now that she's 4!  I love the Christian message it sends to her through song. I would highly recommend this video!

Being a Christian, I wanted to have this for my granddaughter.  She is 2 and she loved it for a while but it drove my daughter crazy.  Miss Pattycake spends her whole time staring at the camera and I would not want to be a kid doing a show with her.  She seems overly whatever.  Annoying for adults, loved by 2 year olds.
